channel.title: Can SomeOne Please Make A WebClient For Me?
channel.description: I really need a webclient for my server. I have a client that is made, but I can't figure out how to turn it into a webclient. I tried Ric's WebClient Tutorial. I also tried another way, but it wouldn't work. Could someone please make one for me or give me the URL for a good webclient tutorial?
